{"tid":797156,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本地插畫師「馬屎」逝世　終年50歲　曾負責港鐵漫畫風海報設計","createTime":"2018-08-28T09:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T09:54:52.000Z","uid":188112,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"abc8f61fd35a9e483e2c1a5c5cf67f7367f64471","tid":797156,"uid":188112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:46:03.000Z","msg":"人稱「馬屎」的本地插畫師Thomas Ho，於周日（26日）早上在家中猝逝，終年50歲。<br />\n<br />\n「馬屎」生前好友、同為插畫家的Tom Lau，向《明報》轉述「馬屎」的兄長所言，指「馬屎」21年前曾罹患鼻咽癌，但治癒後一直沒有復發，近期也沒有特別長期病患，故其逝世可能因突發隱性病，目前仍在確認中。<br />\n<br />\nTom Lau讚揚「馬屎」是自己從事插畫工作30年以來，在香港所見過「畫人及描繪能力最叻的人」。<br />\n<br />\n「馬屎」曾與多家本地企業合作，屢有獲獎。而他近期知名作品，則是與港鐵合作的一系列漫畫風格海報。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180828/s00001/1535443977658\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180828%2Fs00001%2F1535443977658&d=yWPJG85ZHa9pNZf8Pcydo2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=5eca4d99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180828%2Fs00001%2F1535443977658&h=9a465cc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180828/s00001/1535443977658</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/174505_a5237875159c75088862e8e28ba1e860.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F174505_a5237875159c75088862e8e28ba1e860.png&h=f7ded09d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/174539_84204df6547f7b91ce9d002e1a7fb2c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F174539_84204df6547f7b91ce9d002e1a7fb2c7.png&h=7726f323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/174543_1e867f44d9821efcaec409a869339c3e.png\" data-thumbna